Executive Vice President, Worldwide Field Operations at VERITAS, cordially
invites you to be our guest at the 2001 U.S. Open Championship.


Watch the world's best golfers compete for the most coveted title on the
tour at the historic Southern Hills Country Club in Tulsa, Oklahoma.


VERITAS has arranged especially for you, some of the most exquisite dining
experiences available featuring unique culinary delights found only in
Tulsa.


In addition to full hospitality in an air-conditioned tent next to the
Admission Gate, VERITAS will provide:


*	Hospitality tent at a private facility with a panoramic view
of the 11th green and 12th fairway

*	Airline Ticket to and from the event*

*	Transportation to and from the airport

*	Accommodations for two nights

*	Breakfast

*	Luncheon

*	Dinner

*	Daily pairing sheets, official programs and daily newspaper

*	Outdoor patio area with umbrella tables

*	Fully stocked open bar

*	Tickets to the event

*	Shuttle service to/from the entrance gate (5 minute trip)

*	Complimentary golf lessons from a teaching professional

*	Complimentary golf simulator/virtual golf

*	Tee times**

This invitation is non-transferable. Limited spots are available. Please
RSVP as soon as possible to: cbailey@veritas.com
<mailto:cbailey@veritas.com>

Please contact Cindy Bailey if you have questions or require additional
information.


* Travel and accommodations must be arranged through VERITAS travel service
by June 1, 2001
** Please reserve at time of RSVP. Subject to Availability.


